fulltitle: John J. McCloy & The Warren Commission: Black Op Radio
title: John J. McCloy & The Warren Commission: Black Op Radio
_filename: _John J. McCloy & The Warren Commission - Black Op Radio.webm
description: Jim DiEugenio and Len Osanic discuss Warren Commission member John J. McCloy. Prior to his sitting on the Warren Commission, John J. McCloy was infamous for his involvement with Nazi war criminals and his implementation of Japanese internment in the United States.
